						               													<description>Everyone loves animals, especially puppies! But you even more so. And that's why you're off to the world's most exotic destinations in search of the cutest little ones.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rainbow Pets is a cute, simultaneous pick and choose game where you play together, with a turn-based pick and bluff mechanism.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players, each turn, choose six puppies to bet on with inverted tokens, to vote hidden: three of them (depicting a paw on one side) are real, while the remaining (blank) are bluffs. When all players have finished their tokens, they proceed to reveal them; bluffs are discarded. If only one player has a valid token on the card, the puppy is adopted by the owner, adding at the end of the game the victory points indicated at the top of the card. If several tokens are placed on the puppy card by different players, the puppy is cuddled, producing the effect shown at the bottom of the card. Adopted puppies are replaced in the same number by other cards. The winner is the one who, at the end of three rounds, has the most victory points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
